# =====================================================
# MOVALAB ENVIRONMENT CONFIGURATION
# =====================================================
# Self-hosted with local Supabase (Docker)
#
# SETUP:
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.local.template .env.local
#   2. Install Docker Desktop
#   3. Run: npm run setup
#   4. Run: npm run dev
#   5. Open: http://localhost:3000
#   6. Follow the setup wizard to create your superadmin account

